Package model

Class Party

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Party

  • public class Party
extends Object
    Author:
    Kylie The class Party represents a single political party, with its own name, projected number of seats, and projected percentage of votes. In addition to the getter and setter methods for the three instance variables listed above, methods are included for formatting the output information, calculating the percentage of seats a party is expected to win, and visualization of the seats and votes for a party.
